OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FIran has reversed course on reopening
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, reimposing
OL,8,Frestrictions on the critical waterway
OL,9,Fafter the US said it would not end its
OL,10,Fblockade of the Islamic Republic's
OL,11,Fports.
OL,13,FThe country's joint military command
OL,14,Fsaid "control of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,15,Fhas returned to its previous state...
OL,16,Funder strict management and control of
OL,17,Fthe armed forces".
OL,26,@vD@FOUyD@QO]
