PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776564202
OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FIt warned that it would continue to
OL,7,Fblock transit through the strait as
OL,8,Flong as the US blockade of Iranian
OL,9,Fports remained in effect.
OL,11,FThe announcement came the morning
OL,12,Fafter US President Donald Trump said
OL,13,Fthe American blockade "will remain in
OL,14,Ffull force" until Tehran reaches a
OL,15,Fdeal with the US, including on its
OL,16,Fnuclear program.
OL,26,@uD@WOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
