PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776564202
OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FSpeaking at a diplomatic forum in
OL,7,FAntalya, Turkey, Pakistan's Foreign
OL,8,FMinister Ishaq Dar said the separate
OL,9,Fceasefire in Lebanon was a positive
OL,10,Fsign.
OL,12,FHe noted that fighting between Israel
OL,13,Fand Hezbollah had been a key sticking
OL,14,Fpoint before talks in Islamabad ended
OL,15,F"very close" to an agreement last
OL,16,Fweekend.
OL,18,FPakistan is expected to host a second
OL,19,Fround of talks between Iran and the US
OL,20,Fearly next week.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@LO]
