OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776564202
OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FQuestions remain over Lebanon truce
OL,8,FWhile mediators have been optimistic,
OL,9,Fit is unclear to what extent Hezbollah
OL,10,Fwill abide by the truce between the
OL,11,FLebanese and Israeli governments.
OL,13,FThe militant group did not play a role
OL,14,Fin ceasefire talks and has previously
OL,15,Fsaid it would not recognise the
OL,16,Flegitimacy of the negotiations, which
OL,17,Fhave allowed Israel to continue
OL,18,Foccupying a stretch of southern
OL,19,FLebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
