PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776564202
OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FTrump said in another post that Israel
OL,7,Fis "prohibited" by the US from further
OL,8,Fstrikes on Lebanon and that "enough is
OL,9,Fenough" in the Israel-Hezbollah war.
OL,11,FThe State Department said the
OL,12,Fprohibition applies only to offensive
OL,13,Fattacks and not to actions taken in
OL,14,Fself-defence.
OL,26,@oD@DOUoD@OO]pD@]OUqD@GO]
