OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776564202
OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FShortly before Trump's post, Israeli
OL,7,FPrime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu said
OL,8,FIsrael agreed to the ceasefire in
OL,9,FLebanon "at the request of my friend
OL,10,FPresident Trump," but that the
OL,11,Fcampaign against Hezbollah is not
OL,12,Fcomplete.
OL,14,FHe claimed Israel had destroyed about
OL,15,F90% of Hezbollah's missile and rocket
OL,16,Fstockpiles and added that Israeli
OL,17,Fforces "have not finished yet" with
OL,18,Fthe dismantling of the group.
OL,26,@qD@IOUrD@QO]yD@HOUyD@^O]
