OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FIn Beirut, displaced families began
OL,7,Fmoving toward southern Lebanon and
OL,8,FBeirut's southern suburbs despite
OL,9,Fwarnings by officials not to return to
OL,10,Ftheir homes until it became clear
OL,11,Fwhether the ceasefire would hold.
OL,13,FThe Lebanese army and UN peacekeepers
OL,14,Fin southern Lebanon reported sporadic
OL,15,Fartillery shelling in some parts of
OL,16,Fsouthern Lebanon in the hours after
OL,17,Fthe ceasefire took effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
