OL,3,CIran closes Strait of Hormuz again in
OL,4,Cresponse to US blockade on its ports
OL,6,FThe war, which began with US and
OL,7,FIsraeli strikes on February 28 has
OL,8,Fkilled at least 3,000 people in Iran,
OL,9,Fmore than 2,290 in Lebanon, 23 in
OL,10,FIsrael and more than a dozen in Gulf
OL,11,FArab states. Meanwhile 13 US service
OL,12,Fmembers have been killed.
